---
title: Tex-Mex Protein Shreds and Rice Skillet with Cheddar Cheese
description: This colourful, no-fuss Tex-Mex skillet is packed with flavour thanks to spiced rice and salsa-coated protein shreds and peppers. Melty cheese and a dollop of sour cream are all you need to make your tastebuds sing!
